Supervisory Organization is a fundamental organization type withing Workday HCM

- Are required and critically important to HCM - all workers are hired into a Supervisory Org
- Group Workers into a management hierarchy to specify - who reports to whom
- Supervisory Organizations "report" to one another to form the Supervisory Org Hieracrchy
- Each Supervisory Org has one and only one superior (parent) organization
- Provide the context for staffing actions
- Each worker is a "member" of a Supervisory Org
- A manager (role) is "assigned" to a Supervisory Org or may be inherited from a superior org
- A manager is "NOT a member" of the orgs they manage
